{"tid":1329113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集結] 721就算你出唔到去都可以幫手打輿論戰","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T00:13:16.000Z","uid":216800,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"973fc7ea27f02df8dcfedcbb0c1cad28cf6e1a8c","tid":1329113,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:12:39.000Z","msg":"今次運動所有人都有自己能力可以做到既野<br />\n唔好覺得自己因為一D野而出唔到去遊行 覺得自己幫唔到大家<br />\n依加我話比你知!!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲有野可以做!!</span></span><br />\n勇武既衝<br />\n和理既擋<br />\n鍵盤打輿論<br />\n如果覺得3樣野都做唔到 你仲可以按<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分享</span><br />\n將消息不停轉發傳出去 你都可以對運動起到好大作用!!<br />\n記住!!  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">盡自己所能!! <span style=\"color: red;\">每一個人既付出都係幫緊香港!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議議員唔好再阻止晒<br />\n真係想幫就幫手擋動物 幫手救返被拉既人 而唔係擋自己人!"},{"pid":"ef1e20c952016bdf64ced60c07ebaaf7fe4f5942","tid":1329113,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79d6db1d343e1e5cdb5f08fc8151ce51d4eb6c2","tid":1329113,"uid":249526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:18:47.000Z","msg":"721無理由唔出去"},{"pid":"16b0b4c12b43bb30740018058c8d7affd914f38c","tid":1329113,"uid":216800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ce4cf1b286be5102d6391bbfbf35eaa1ab4cc5","tid":1329113,"uid":130438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"出唔到去既手足都出力"},{"pid":"df879e22873a795d70c1022a1b550558c858887e","tid":1329113,"uid":216800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f79d6db1d343e1e5cdb5f08fc8151ce51d4eb6c2","tid":1329113,"uid":249526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:18:4